大的棕榈树和茂密的绿色植被，阳光透过树叶在路面上投下斑驳的阴影。路边还竖立着一个黄色的菱形交通标志，提示前方有弯道。\n*   **远景：** 远处可以看到连绵起伏的山脉轮廓，与海天一色。\n\n**天空与光线：**\n天空呈现出清澈的湛蓝色，点缀着几朵洁白的云彩。阳光明媚，整个画面色彩鲜艳，给人一种宁静、放松的度假氛围。"]},{"id":2,"type":"QwenVL_ModelLoader","pos":[-1635.7051063178671,-531.2719993592145],"size":[270,178],"flags":{},"order":1,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"模型家族","name":"模型家族","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"模型家族"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"主模型","name":"主模型","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"主模型"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"视觉投影mmproj","name":"视觉投影mmproj","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"视觉投影mmproj"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"启用思考","name":"启用思考","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"启用思考"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"上下文长度","name":"上下文长度","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"上下文长度"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"GPU层数","name":"GPU层数","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"GPU层数"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"qwen模型","name":"qwen模型","type":"QWENLLAMA","links":[1]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"QwenVL_ModelLoader"},"widgets_values":["Qwen3.5-VL","Qwen3.5\\Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-IQ4_NL.gguf","Qwen3.5\\mmproj-F32.gguf",true,8192,-1]}],"links":[[1,2,0,1,0,"QWENLLAMA"],[2,3,0,1,1,"IMAGE"],[3,1,0,4,0,"STRING"],[4,4,0,5,0,"STRING"]],"groups":[],"config":{},"extra":{"workflowRendererVersion":"LG","ds":{"scale":0.7237921531946642,"offset":[2455.9968210791176,808.2981782215381]}},"version":0.4}